hopobject.body: I'm on holiday purchase flagyl 500mg online SIR – Paul Harrison (Letters, August 26) referred to brambling and bramble pies, but lives in Essex. This is a subject of great divide in my household. My wife, who is from Suffolk with a Leicester mother, insists on calling the fruit blackberries, and the plants they grow on, brambles. I am from the North East, with a Scottish mother, and call the fruit brambles, which grow on bramble bushes.
